answer.feedback: Pay is too low, I can't do this again.

I hope that missing too many of the 'gold standard' questions doesn't result in a rejection! I did my best, but on some of them I was not sure whether having a full black cap on the head instead of some white meant it was an entirely different species or not. Birds often have a lot of sexual dimorphism, so they just could have been males versus females.

I hope we are not punished for our ignorance of these birds.
Nice survey. Like to participate in more surveys like this.
But what kinds of birds were they?
